{"type": "article", "id": 25372, "title": "吸尘器概念", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-13T07:14:55Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 43, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702120455vMm6L7JQ1KV5INwe.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这款吸尘器的概念设计来自美国设计师 Scott Pancioli，吸头是一个圆环，相当于使用一次有两次的效果。圆环吸头和手柄的倾斜角度经过了调整，当手拿着吸尘器时，不会因为用力下压而断裂。流线的外形黑白色搭配让这款吸尘器设计很简洁，也能更加融入现代家居生活的环境中。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120452ntGZkh06M18XRI3x.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.69047619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120453U9Y5b6XvDWlq7h2n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.49428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021204531SYqiGkZPgoKen68.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70952381\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120454JQ8NTXZKumVgY65o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.54666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120454eL2XMRbxj4Orum3s.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61904762\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}